thread.title: Demonstrators flood Barcelona in support of jailed separatist leaders

title: Demonstrators flood Barcelona in support of jailed separatist leaders
text:
Demonstrators flood Barcelona in support of jailed separatist leaders 3:56pm BST - 00:51 
Catalan protesters call for the return of jailed sepratist leaders and wave banners that say 'Puigdemont President.' Rough cut (no reporter narration).
